# Per-user Sway overrides. The system config at /etc/sway/config already
# establishes the monochrome palette, bindings, and bar. Anything placed in
# this file *extends* the system defaults (Sway honours ~/.config/sway/config
# if present; symlink this file there via `home-manager` or a login script).

# Example: open the CAM transcript overlay on workspace 2 automatically.
# for_window [app_id="cam-overlay"] move container to workspace number 2
